Optional reference backend (NOT part of the default distribution):

  The project can be built with an optional Swiss Ephemeris reference
  backend (`make vendor-swiss`, backend="swiss") used only for
  cross-implementation verification. Swiss Ephemeris and pyswisseph are
  licensed by Astrodienst AG under the AGPL-3.0 (or a commercial license)
  and are NOT redistributed with AstroText: no Swiss Ephemeris code or
  data is committed to this repository or included in released wheels.
  The name "Swiss Ephemeris" appears here and in the sources only
  factually, to describe that verification reference. The default
  distribution is verified Swiss-Ephemeris-free by tools/check_no_swiss.py.
